OOC: Okay, I've been under a lot of pressure on keeping Stalker alive, so 
I'll give it a rest. I shoudn't have thought I could ever escape from the 
Alliance alive.  Zardus, Unitron?  Were you planning this while Soundwave was 
alive and well talking peace?

::Stalkers spark joins the matrix.  His last thought was that he died 
protecting the peace::

Please put him on the deceased list,  killed by Nemesis Enforcer, Dark One, 
Breakdown, and Scattershot.  I'm sorry i moded a bit but that was because I 
really liked this character.
